Timi Dakolo is celebrating his son, Alex Dakolo, who turned a year oldr today, September 6, 2019. Sharing this new photo of them posing together, the singer wrote: ‘HAPPY BIRTHDAY TO THE CHAIRMAN OF THE YARD PEOPLE.MAY THE GRACE OF GOD CONTINUE TO SURROUND YOU,THE PEACE OF GOD KEEP YOU AND I PRONOUNCE THE GOODNESS OF GOD UPON YOUR LIFE.LONG LIFE WILL MY SON.HAPPY BIRTHDAY MY SON.’